   <conbody>
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Start a web browser from a PC on the same network as the gateway.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the IP address that is configured for the gateway in
the address field.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the default login information:<sl class="- topic/sl ">
                  <sli class="- topic/sli ">
                     <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">User name: </b>Administrator</sli>
                  <sli class="- topic/sli ">
