            </p>
            <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">The user name and password must be
changed after the first login.</note>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">To change the login information navigate to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Configuration
&gt; Authentication</uicontrol> in the side menu.</p>
